<p />
<u style="text-underline-offset: 5px;">TOGGLE COLUMNS (on/off)</u>: <div id="column-toggle-container"></div>
<p />ADJUST COLUMN POSITIONS: select the column header cell and drag it where you want. <strong><a href="https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/images/column-drag6.gif" rel="lightbox">show me!</a></strong>
